Privacy Policy for NEXSCAN.AI
Effective Date: [13/04/2026]
1. Information Collection NEXSCAN.AI uses the device's Camera to provide document scanning features. Images captured are processed locally or used for conversion as per user request. We do not store your personal photos on our servers.
2. AI Features (Gemini API) When you use the AI Hub to analyze documents, the text extracted from your PDF is sent to Google's Gemini API for processing. This data is not used by us for training or tracking.
3. Permissions
•
Camera: Required for scanning documents.
•
Storage: Required to save and load PDF files.
4. Advertising We use Google AdMob to show ads. AdMob may collect device identifiers to serve personalized ads.
5. Contact Us For any questions, contact us at: [gamezycreations@gmail.com]
